o.nz/pages/contact\" style=\"font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; font-weight:500;\" target=\"_blank\">Contact Us</a></td>\n</tr></table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Hero -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#f5f5f5; border-bottom:3px solid #CC1B2A;\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:36px 32px 28px;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#CC1B2A; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px;\">Replenishment Reminder</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin:0 0 10px; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:30px; font-weight:bold; color:#222222; line-height:1.2;\">Time to reorder your Regaine, {{ first_name|default:'there' }}?</h1>\n<p style=\"margin:0; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:15px; color:#666666;\">Consistency is the key \u2014 don't break your routine now.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Body -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:32px 40px 24px; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16px; color:#333333; line-height:1.7;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 20px;\">Hi {{ first_name|default:'there' }},</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 20px;\">Based on your last Regaine order, you may be running low. Hair loss treatment works best when used consistently \u2014 don't let a gap in supply set back your progress.</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 28px;\">Restock today and keep your routine on track. We have New Zealand's best prices on Regaine \u2014 and if you find it cheaper anywhere else, we'll beat it by 10%.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#CC1B2A; border-radius:4px;\">\n<a href=\"https://www.bargainchemist.co.nz/collections/hair-loss\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:14px 36px; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:bold; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_blank\">Reorder Regaine \u2192</a>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Why consistent reminder -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9; border-top:1px solid #eeeeee; border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee;\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:24px 40px; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#555555; line-height:1.6;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px; font-weight:bold; color:#333333;\">Why consistent use matters:</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">\u2713 \u00a0Regaine requires consistent daily use to maintain results</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;\">\u2713 \u00a0Results can reverse if treatment is stopped</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;\">\u2713 \u00a0Most users see best results after 4+ months of regular use</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:20px 40px 32px; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:#888888; line-height:1.5; text-align:center;\">\n          *Always read the label. Use only as directed. If symptoms persist, see your healthcare professional.\n        </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Footer: Get social -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:9px 18px; font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:bold; color:#222222; text-align:center;\">\n        Get social with us!\n      </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Footer: Social icons -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:9px;\">\n<a href=\"https://tiktok.com/@